Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自由騎士潘恩的活躍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克等人成功地\N由暗妖精手中保住了餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.56,0:00:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻因暗妖精卑鄙的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而再度陷入新的危機中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.66,0:00:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我幹的好事…真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.23,0:00:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算玩到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快點把餅乾搶過來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.61,0:00:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修拉姆大人，真是對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.18,0:00:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，飯桶一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.75,0:00:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，阿修拉姆大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂德!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.79,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來救我了是嗎，蒂德!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂德!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.59,0:00:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!弄錯人了，放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇!\N你要對我的比蘿絲做什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.30,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開!快放開啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認錯人啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂德、蒂德、蒂德!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.64,0:01:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭!好噁心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.24,0:01:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手啊!\N笨蛋!醜男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.99,0:01:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 咦?\N- 怎麼會又…哇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.19,0:01:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?原來是你飛起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.19,0:01:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快來救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 蒂德、蒂德、蒂德…\N- 咦?那個臭男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂德、蒂德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝你，龍寶寶\N- 得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大白癡勇者!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好像做得太過火了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
